function createDeprecatedProperties (path, props) {
  const obj = {}

  Object.keys(props).forEach(name => {
    lazy(obj, name, () => {
      warnOnce(`math.${path}.${name} is moved to math.${name} in v6.0.0. ` +
        'Please use the new location instead.')
      return props[name]
    })
  })

  return obj
}
